  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为HealthTech系统画一个批处理作业的状态流转图。起点是PatientRecords模块，数据以Batch的形式进入系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[HealthTech_PatientRecords]",
        "Batch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以PatientRecords是起始状态。那Batch进入系统后，第一个事件是Received吗？然后进入Started状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Batch.Received.Event",
        "Batch.Started.State"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Batch.Received触发后进入Started状态。然后每个Batch会拆分成多个Job，所以下一步是Job.Received.Event。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Batch.Started.State",
        "Job.Received.Event"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上了Job的流转：Job.Received.Event到Job.Received.State，然后完成时触发Job.Completed.Event。这里正常结束和异常分支都要画吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Job.Received.State",
        "Job.Completed.Event",
        "Job.Failed.Event"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "都要。正常流程是Job.Completed.State之后汇聚到Batch.Job.Done.Event，最终到达Finished状态，输出到LabAnalyzer。失败的话，Job.Failed.State要走到Batch.Job.Done.Failed.Event，然后到Batch.Failed.State，输出到DiagnosticEngine。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Job.Completed.State",
        "Batch.Job.Done.Event",
        "Batch.Finished.State",
        "[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]",
        "Job.Failed.State",
        "Batch.Job.Done.Failed.Event",
        "Batch.Failed.State",
        "[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：LabAnalyzer接收成功完成的Batch，DiagnosticEngine处理失败的Batch。那LabAnalyzer会反向触发什么事件吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]",
        "[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，LabAnalyzer如果处理不了，会触发Batch.Received.Failed.Event，这个也走向Batch.Failed.State。相当于一个回环，让失败的Batch也能进入诊断引擎。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]",
        "Batch.Received.Failed.Event",
        "Batch.Failed.State"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个图覆盖了从PatientRecords进入，经过Batch和Job的多层状态流转，最终根据成功或失败分别输出到LabAnalyzer或DiagnosticEngine，也包括LabAnalyzer返回失败的回环路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
